{"tid":2307875,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工會難阻罷工醫護被扣薪","createTime":"2020-12-01T12:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T12:45:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"325c5480998f8d1b4aac89107b8d1b36be49e0cf","tid":2307875,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/4F7WBA4X6VATJN66TIC23QRWW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F4F7WBA4X6VATJN66TIC23QRWW4%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0nG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=c0300731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F4F7WBA4X6VATJN66TIC23QRWW4%2F&h=4b2628e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/4F7WBA4X6VATJN66TIC23QRWW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n工會難阻罷工醫護被扣薪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4ABtBTuEQ74H_a9NBvJKimUVnQs=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AYAJALW7RNDIFJDGNLJALDT5AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4ABtBTuEQ74H_a9NBvJKimUVnQs%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAYAJALW7RNDIFJDGNLJALDT5AY.jpg&h=c2a75cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余慧明指在法律層面無法阻止醫管局扣除罷工醫護薪金的處分。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】醫管局員工陣線今年2月初發動罷工救港行動，至少7,000名員工響應。醫管局一度疑追究罷工的醫護，惟最終決定扣除今年2月3日至7日期間缺勤的員工薪金，並不會就此作出其他人力資源方面的跟進。醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明昨指，不認同扣除罷工醫護薪金作為處分方式，但徵詢法律團隊意見後，工會在法律層面無法阻止局方做法。<br />\n<br />\n余慧明認為局方是因為。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀與醫管局公開談判<br />\n<br />\n余慧明指，在法律層面無法阻止醫管局扣除罷工醫護薪金的處分，並強調重點為「罷工唔係缺勤」，不能以缺勤形容其工業行動，並已發表聲明，期望能與醫管局公開談判。她解釋，在人力資源層面而言，缺勤屬紀律問題，若然主管採取紀律處分，則屬行政上秋後算賬的行為。"}]}